Dialogue: 5,0:00:05.41,0:00:06.20,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:06.66,0:00:10.07,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought he'd committed suicide.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.60,0:00:14.01,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't such a coward.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:14.01,0:00:17.97,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He was a guy who'd just grit his teeth and do the best he could when faced with adversity.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:18.40,0:00:21.09,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You'd never hear him complaining.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.09,0:00:22.43,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.84,0:00:27.29,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Even when everyone was asleep, he'd be up drawing something.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:29.29,0:00:32.10,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Moritaka, have you read "Star of the Giants"?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:32.10,0:00:34.05,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.98,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Then you know that one line of Ryoma Sakamoto's?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:37.37,0:00:38.04,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:38.83,0:00:40.85,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You always did love "Ashita no Joe".
Dialogue: 5,0:00:42.90,0:00:43.46,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.85,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, I think I get it.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:47.51,0:00:48.68,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:49.21,0:00:50.11,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.07,Default,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.29,0:00:58.10,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's her mom! This has to be Azuki's mom!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:59.50,0:01:04.82,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cheer you on from the sidelines while you work on becoming excellent manga artists.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:04.82,0:01:06.76,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:06.76,0:01:07.79,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:08.15,0:01:10.66,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty lucky.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:10.66,0:01:12.57,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't just you, it's us!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:12.80,0:01:15.22,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely make this dream a reality!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.22,0:01:17.15,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't do this...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:18.11,0:01:19.41,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be a real man!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:20.55,0:01:21.60,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a man yet!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:22.66,0:01:23.68,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.73,Default,Saiko,0000,0000,0000,,No— Today, I'm gonna work on my own manga drawing style.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:26.73,0:01:29.31,Default,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'm gonna work hard on names!
